{"id": "art-2441", "label": "Art. 2441", "title": "Art. 2441: Informarea privind condiţiile speciale de executare a reţinerii şi arestării preventive dispuse faţă de minor", "slug": "art-2441", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2018153328\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2129\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2018153328\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 244<sup>1</sup>:\nInformarea privind condi&#355;iile speciale de executare a re&#355;inerii\n&#351;i arest&#259;rii preventive dispuse fa&#355;&#259; de minor </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1269455928\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2128\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1269455928\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; persoana re&#355;inut&#259; sau arestat&#259;\neste minor, odat&#259; cu informarea prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 209 alin. (17)\n&#351;i art. 228 alin. (2), acesteia i se comunic&#259; &#351;i dreptul la\ncondi&#355;ii speciale de executare, potrivit art. 244.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_378494138\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2127\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_378494138\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Informarea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se face\n&#351;i c&#259;tre p&#259;rin&#355;i sau, dup&#259; caz, tutore, curator ori\npersoana în îngrijirea sau supravegherea c&#259;reia se afl&#259; temporar\nminorul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1445099933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2126\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1445099933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; p&#259;rin&#355;ii sau, dup&#259; caz,\ntutorele, curatorul ori persoana în îngrijirea sau supravegherea c&#259;reia se\nafl&#259; temporar minorul nu au putut fi g&#259;si&#355;i ori informarea\nacestora ar afecta interesul superior al minorului sau desf&#259;&#351;urarea\nprocesului penal, informarea se va face c&#259;tre un alt adult care este\ndesemnat de minor &#351;i acceptat în aceast&#259; calitate de organul\njudiciar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1707969362\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2125\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1707969362\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care minorul nu desemneaz&#259; un alt adult\nconform alin. (3) sau adultul desemnat nu este acceptat de organul judiciar,\ninformarea se va face c&#259;tre o alt&#259; persoan&#259; aleas&#259; de\norganul judiciar, &#355;inând seama de interesul superior al minorului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_551779229\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2124\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_551779229\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul în care circumstan&#355;ele prev&#259;zute la\nalin. (3) sau (4) înceteaz&#259;, informarea se va face potrivit alin. (2).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL II:Aplicarea provizorie a\nm&#259;surilor de siguran&#355;&#259; cu caracter medical</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 1:Obligarea provizorie la\ntratament medical</span></b></p>"}